==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subduplicate
<hw>Sub*du"pli*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Math.)</fld>
<def>Expressed by the square root; -- said of ratios.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Subduplicate ratio</b></col>, <cd>the ratio of the square
roots, or the square root of a ratio; <as>thus, the <ex>subduplicate
ratio</ex> of <it>a</it> to <it>b</it> is ⟦root⟧<it>a</it> to
⟦root⟧<it>b</it>, or
⟦root⟧<fract><it>a</it>/<it>b</it></fract></as>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subdural</ent>⟦br⟧
